# hexa-lang /.roadmap — project roadmap SSOT
# Declarative phase/track/milestone registry. raw#15 enforced.
# Format spec: self/raw_loader.hexa (same grammar as .raw / .own / .ext)
#
# Format:
#   roadmap <id> <status> "<name>"
#     track    <bootstrap|self-host|native|perf|ssot|...>
#     phase    <P0|P1|P7-6|...>
#     status   <planned|active|done|blocked|deferred>
#     eta      <YYYY-MM-DD or TBD>
#     <key>    <value>
#
# status (locked, 5): live warn new deferred convention
# required keys: track phase eta why
# standard keys (common): owner proof note deprecated-at depends-on unblocks

roadmap 1 convention "example — replace with real roadmap entries"
  track     placeholder
  phase     P0
  eta       TBD
  why       .roadmap skeleton — replace with real phases when migrating from shared/roadmaps/*.json
